swap.desc: For your better understanding of the Swap Free Program, we've provided explanations for these terms below.
swap.desc_date: Displayed from the perspective of the date, the amount deducted from swap for each order is displayed on a daily settlement basis.
swap.desc_level: This shows your current swap-free level
swap.desc_level_duration: This shows your current swap-free level duration
swap.desc_order: Display the total swap fee charged for each order, including the position-holding period and daily Swap charged amount.
swap.desc_record: In order to understand the swap cost of account transactions, dcfx labuan displays the detailed data of swap charged by the account in two modes.
swap.desc_swap: Swap refers to the overnight fee incurred by your orders
swap.desc_swap_free: Displays the swap adjustments on your overnight positions due to the swap-free policy. Positive numbers indicate swap saved due to the policy, while negative figures are for record-keeping, showing the exempted swap amount with no actual cost incurred.
swap.desc_trading_activity: This shows your current trading activity percentage

detail.placholder: Display the detailed swap records generated by each transaction order during the period.
detail.tip_date: Display the detailed swap records generated by the date. The swap shown below is the actual swap amount charged.
detail.tip_order: Display the detailed swap records generated by each order. The swap shown below is the actual swap amount charged.
